VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT allowRunningInsecureContent\s*:\s*true
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:allowRunningInsecureContent:\s*true && MISSING:test|development|localhost
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects Electron configurations that allow loading insecure (HTTP) content in HTTPS pages.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for allowRunningInsecureContent Enabled.
